1
00:00:53,820 --> 00:00:55,700
That is what my dad drinks every single night.

2
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:01,260
You should pay no attention to it.

3
00:01:06,110 --> 00:01:07,400
But I want to try it.

4
00:01:11,260 --> 00:01:12,690
It is highly inappropriate.

5
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:14,700
I wasn’t asking for permission.

6
00:01:15,390 --> 00:01:16,560
I'm going to steal it.

7
00:01:18,470 --> 00:01:21,150
You mean you're going to steal the liquor of..

8
00:01:21,180 --> 00:01:23,330
Go distract my dad,

9
00:01:24,290 --> 00:01:25,960
and I will grab the bottle myself.

10
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:35,090
No.

11
00:01:36,870 --> 00:01:37,930
I will not do.

12
00:01:40,010 --> 00:01:44,900
In that case, I suppose I’ll just have to tell dad

13
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:53,070
that my bodyguard has been acting inappropriately.

14
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,420
Only once...

15
00:02:32,980 --> 00:02:33,840
Lord,

16
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:38,380
I have a matter to consult with you about.

17
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:46,710
Hold on.

18
00:02:48,710 --> 00:02:49,800
Pour me some water first.

19
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,440
Yes,sir.

20
00:03:19,420 --> 00:03:20,760
Now, what is it?

21
00:03:21,110 --> 00:03:27,290
Well... it is about the night shift, sir.

22
00:03:27,940 --> 00:03:29,540
Lately, I feel like the guards…

23
00:03:48,410 --> 00:03:49,690
Want some more, Kaew?

24
00:03:51,210 --> 00:03:52,360
I’ll refill it for you.

25
00:03:57,820 --> 00:03:59,540
I’ve drink enough.

26
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:01,710
And you too.

27
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:09,250
No, I’m not drunk yet!

28
00:04:17,870 --> 00:04:19,280
Don't touch me.

29
00:04:21,270 --> 00:04:22,560
But you're about to fall.

30
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,440
I am not falling!

31
00:04:32,730 --> 00:04:34,680
I literally just caught you.

32
00:04:37,580 --> 00:04:42,850
In that case... I suppose you will just have to keep catching me forever, then.

33
00:04:57,520 --> 00:05:01,290
I have something to ask you.

34
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,290
Kaew,

35
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:10,570
in all the time we have spent together...

36
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:14,900
Do you feel the same way I do?

37
00:05:17,290 --> 00:05:21,980
I have never felt this way about anyone before.

38
00:05:24,100 --> 00:05:25,790
Only you.

39
00:05:34,910 --> 00:05:37,230
But... you might not truly know who I really am.

40
00:05:42,320 --> 00:05:46,410
I know everything about you.

41
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:53,020
Including your true identity.

42
00:06:36,220 --> 00:06:38,540
As long as you are in my room,

43
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:54,950
everything will be a secret between the two of us, forever.

44
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:06,320
Are you drunk, Kaew?

45
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:14,330
When you wake up tomorrow,

46
00:07:16,700 --> 00:07:19,690
will you remember what happened tonight?

47
00:07:24,590 --> 00:07:29,260
I will remember the story of tonight forever.

48
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:43,900
Can you help me, Kaew?

49
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:52,320
Will you remember what happened tonight?

50
00:08:55,420 --> 00:09:00,700
I will remember the story of tonight forever.

51
00:09:46,640 --> 00:09:48,300
Are you sure?

52
00:09:52,210 --> 00:09:53,800
Please help me, Kaew.

53
00:11:05,470 --> 00:11:06,810
How do you feel?

54
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,700
I feel good.

55
00:11:14,850 --> 00:11:18,360
Should I help you with something?

56
00:11:21,490 --> 00:11:26,670
Tonight, I only want to make you happy.

57
00:11:30,630 --> 00:11:35,810
If you are happy, I am happy.

58
00:12:25,620 --> 00:12:27,390
Why didn't you ask me to come down with you?

59
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:33,480
I saw you were asleep, so I didn't want to wake you.

60
00:12:43,190 --> 00:12:47,120
You know, before this, my life was so boring.

61
00:12:47,930 --> 00:12:49,930
Day after day, I just stayed in the house,

62
00:12:50,550 --> 00:12:52,250
doing the same things every single day.

63
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,810
I couldn't change a thing.

64
00:12:55,930 --> 00:12:57,930
Everything was already predetermined.

65
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:04,830
But ever since you came into my life, everything changed.

66
00:13:06,450 --> 00:13:08,430
You gave me the courage to truly live.

67
00:13:10,560 --> 00:13:13,150
You are like the moon in the night sky...

68
00:13:14,230 --> 00:13:19,280
just like a precious gem, and the light of my life.
